# Turbocharged TeleBots for Instant Outreach!

Turbocharge your Telegram bot messaging with this interactive interface. Easily send SMS-like messages and images to multiple users simultaneously.

## Table of Contents
- [Getting Started](#getting-started)
  - [Prerequisites](#prerequisites)
  - [Usage](#usage)
- [How to Use](#how-to-use)
- [Example Bots](#example-bots)
